Want to know more?

Is Cornerstone a subscription?

Yes, but it's flexible and you're in control. When you sign up you choose a product selection and a delivery frequency and we then regularly send you shaving supplies, charging your card each time we send a fresh box. You can easily alter your product selection, delivery frequency, delay or cancel your plan at any time.

How do I sign up?

Firstly, we'll ask you two quick questions about your shaving routine to make sure we're sending you the right products at the right time. Then we'll take some personal details such as your address and payment details and you're done - the whole process takes 2 minutes and you can do it from your phone, tablet or desktop computer.

Can I give it a try?

Yes, just delay your next order if you don't need it just yet, we won't send you any more shaving supplies or charge your card again without reminding you first. We also offer a 30-Day Money Back Guarantee, so you can give us a try without any risk.

How much does it cost?

Between £14-30 per box depending on which of our products you select. We try our very best to undercut the prices you'll pay on the high street, plus we offer free delivery and a free personalised chrome-plated razor handle when you join, so overall we think Cornerstone is great value.

What if I don't like it?

We're pretty confident that we can improve your daily shave and make life a little more convenient. But, if you don't love your first shave, we'll give you a full refund, no questions asked.
